OL,3,CPhilosophy student to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurder after driving over fiance
OL,6,Fwho ran over her fiance after she
OL,7,F"lost her temper" is due to be
OL,8,Fsentenced for murder.
OL,10,FAlice Wood, 24, claimed her partner
OL,11,FRyan Watson died in a "tragic
OL,12,Faccident" when he was hit by the Ford
OL,13,FFiesta she was driving near their home
OL,14,Fin Rode Heath, Cheshire, at about
OL,15,F11.30pm on May 6 2022.
OL,17,FBut she was found guilty of murder
OL,18,Flast month following a trial at
OL,19,FChester Crown Court and is to be
OL,20,Fsentenced on Friday.
