OL,3,CPhilosophy student to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurder after driving over fiance
OL,6,FThe three-week trial heard the couple
OL,7,Fhad spent the evening at a party in
OL,8,FHanley, Stoke-on-Trent, with staff and
OL,9,Fservice users of the brain injury
OL,10,Fcharity Headway, where Mr Watson was a
OL,11,Fsupport worker.
OL,13,FAndrew Ford KC, prosecuting, said Mr
OL,14,FWatson was seen on CCTV footage
OL,15,F"having a good time, being a
OL,16,Fgregarious and outgoing party guest"
OL,17,Fwhile Wood was described by one woman
OL,18,Fattending as "a bit cold".
