OL,3,CPhilosophy student to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurder after driving over fiance
OL,6,FShe told the court she went out to her
OL,7,Fcar to leave but Mr Watson followed.
OL,9,FDuring his opening address, Mr Ford
OL,10,Fsaid "she lost her temper" and "used
OL,11,Fthe car as a weapon".
OL,13,FThe jury was told Mr Watson was
OL,14,Ftrapped underneath the car as Wood
OL,15,Fdrove 158 metres up Sandbach Road
OL,16,Fbefore stopping.
