OL,3,CPhilosophy student to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cmurder after driving over fiance
OL,6,FThe court heard Wood was preparing for
OL,7,Ffinal exams in a theology, philosophy
OL,8,Fand ethics degree at the time and had
OL,9,Fa scholarship for a part-time research
OL,10,Fmasters at Cambridge.
OL,12,FOn the first day of the trial, she had
OL,13,Fa copy of the book Meditations, a
OL,14,Fphilosophy text by Roman Marcus
OL,15,FAurelius, under her arm as she was led
OL,16,Fin handcuffs from the prison van to
OL,17,Fthe court.
OL,19,FFollowing her conviction, Judge
OL,20,FMichael Leeming warned Wood she "may
OL,21,Fnever be released" from prison.
