OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Watson's family
OL,7,Fsaid it had been "so hard" to
OL,8,Frepeatedly watch the CCTV footage
OL,9,Fshown in court of the moment he was
OL,10,Fkilled while trapped under the car.
OL,12,FThey said: "The one person Ryan
OL,13,Ftrusted the most is the person who
OL,14,Ftook his life in such a violent way.
OL,16,F"Alice is in prison where she belongs
OL,17,Fbut no sentence is going to be long
OL,18,Fenough for what she has taken from us
OL,19,Fand Ryan. He'll never get to live his
OL,20,Flife and fulfil his dreams."
